            <description><![CDATA[【⚠️注意预防！<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E4%B9%B3%E8%85%BA%E7%99%8C%E5%8F%91%E7%97%85%E7%9A%84%E7%9B%B8%E5%85%B3%E5%8D%B1%E9%99%A9%E5%9B%A0%E7%B4%A0%23&amp;extparam=%23%E4%B9%B3%E8%85%BA%E7%99%8C%E5%8F%91%E7%97%85%E7%9A%84%E7%9B%B8%E5%85%B3%E5%8D%B1%E9%99%A9%E5%9B%A0%E7%B4%A0%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#乳腺癌发病的相关危险因素#</span></a>】乳腺癌是女性常见的恶性肿瘤之一，10月18日是世界乳腺癌宣传日。 乳腺癌的高危人群有哪些：①直系亲属中有乳腺癌病史的人群；②基因检查中发现乳腺癌高危基因的人群；③胸部做过放疗的人群等。<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[话筒]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/o_huatong-0a3e80b147.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>医生提醒，乳腺癌的发生一般和雌性激素的异常增加有关👇🏻<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a>（央视网）<a href="http://t.cn/A6WUWXU1" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_web_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span> <span class="surl-text">网页链接</span></a>]]></description>
